title: a mechanism
pid: b2fbf43d-5321-416c-9ab5-2be4c204e13b
body: |2-
  People there tell you,
  "In *this* country we [action] in [situation]",
  when in fact the action-situation pair is universal,
  but in your own country nobody would have said anything,
  because not having your culture to blame it on,
  they just assume you're a weirdo.
